'''特雷沃·大卫·平诺克'''{{CBE}}（{{lang-en|Trevor David Pinnock}}；{{bd|1946年|12月19日||}}），英國[[大鍵琴|大鍵琴]]演奏家、[[指揮家|指揮家]]。以[[復古風格演奏|古樂]]領域的活動，以及與{{link-en|英國古樂團|The English Concert}}的長期合作而聞名。他並曾擔任[[加拿大国家艺术中心乐团|加拿大国家艺术中心乐团]]藝術總監。2003年起，平诺克離開了英國古樂團的專任工作，持續以指揮、大鍵琴演奏的雙重身分活動。此外，他也從事教學工作。

平诺克是英國[[留声机奖|留声机奖]]的得主（指揮歐洲布蘭登堡合奏團，錄製[[约翰·塞巴斯蒂安·巴赫|巴赫]]《[[勃兰登堡协奏曲|勃兰登堡协奏曲]]》）。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
平诺克出生於[[坎特伯雷|坎特伯雷]]，他的祖父在當地經營[[救世軍|救世軍]]的樂隊。父親肯尼斯從事出版，母親喬伊思則是一位業餘歌者<ref name=debrett>{{cite book| date =| author =Pinnock, Trevor David| title =Debrett's People of Today| publisher =Debrett's Peerage Ltd.| isbn =978-1-870520-26-3| url =http://www.knowuk.co.uk/| editor1 =Zöe Gullen| editor2 =Daniel Sefton| access-date =2021-02-13| archive-date =2008-05-16| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20080516081041/http://www.knowuk.co.uk/| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name=australian>{{cite web| url = http://www.hpschd.nu/pr/pr-17.html| title = Born to the baroque| access-date = 2007-04-14| last = Cosic| first = Miriam| date = 2005-07-21| work = The Australian| archive-date = 2006-08-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060819132702/http://www.hpschd.nu/pr/pr-17.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。平诺克一家距離鋼琴家{{link-en|隆納·史密斯 (音樂家)|Ronald Smith (musician)|隆納·史密斯}}的住處不遠，平诺克自小與史密斯的妹妹學習鋼琴。七歲時，他加入了當地的教會合唱團，於1956年至1961年間在合唱學校就讀，之後進入{{link-en|賽門·朗頓男子文法學校|Simon Langton Grammar School for Boys}}<ref name=debrett/><ref>Page, Anne ''Of Choristers, ancient and modern'', [http://www.ofchoristers.net/Chapters/Canterbury.htm  Canterbury, St Edmund’s Junior School] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070514180233/http://www.ofchoristers.net/Chapters/Canterbury.htm |date=14 May 2007 }}. Retrieved 16 February 2010.</ref>。在此他受到鋼琴、管風琴的訓練，並開始在教堂擔任管風琴演奏。十五歲起，他開始接觸大鍵琴演奏<ref name=australian/>。十九歲時，平诺克獲得[[倫敦|倫敦]][[皇家音乐学院_(南肯辛顿)|皇家音乐学院]]獎學金，他前往該校繼續攻讀管風琴與大鍵琴演奏，並獲得獎項肯定<ref name=debrett/><ref name=gramophone>{{cite journal| url = http://www.gramophone.net/Issue/Page/August%202000/15/825271/The+first+time+I+met+Trevor+Pinnock%2C+years+ago+in+the+bar+at+the+Royal+Academy+of+Music%2C+he+let+fall+a+remark+that+Ive+prized+as+a+kernel+of+wisdom+ever+since%2C+a+slogan+of+musical+integrity.+Ive+got+to+the+stage%2C+he+declared+in+response+to+some+naive+question+of+mine%2C+where| title = Direct, blazing simplicity| access-date = 2010-02-15| last = Owen Norris| first = David| date = | journal = Gramophone| page = 15}}{{Dead link|date=July 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。在皇家音樂學院期間，他同{{Link-en|雷夫·多恩斯|Ralph Downes}}與{{Link-en|米利琴特·西爾沃|Millicent Silver}}學習<ref name=crd>Noted in the biography in the liner notes of his recording ''16th Century English Keyboard Music'', CRD records.</ref>。此外，他在課外受[[古斯塔夫·莱昂哈特|古斯塔夫·莱昂哈特]]影響甚多<ref name=gramophone/>。

=== 職業生涯 ===
;從事演奏
平诺克以大鍵琴演奏家的身分與[[圣马丁室内乐团|圣马丁室内乐团]]在歐洲做巡迴<ref name=hutchinson>{{cite book| date =March 2005| author =Pinnock, Trevor| title =Hutchinson Encyclopedia of Britain| publisher =Helicon Publishing| isbn =1-85986-275-6| url =https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofbr0000unse_e8k2}}</ref>{{notetag|皇家音樂學院的老師{{link-en|约翰·斯坦纳|John Stainer}}曾經表示，大鍵琴演奏是不足以維生的工作，對平诺克的前景並不看好<ref name=gramophone/>。}}。1966年，他在[[皇家節日音樂廳|皇家節日音樂廳]]完成職業生涯的倫敦初登場，不過當時是以現代樂器演奏巴洛克曲目<ref name=gramophone/>。1968年則是他的獨奏初登場，地點位於[[普賽爾屋|普賽爾屋]]<ref name=who>{{cite book| date =| author =Pinnock, Trevor| title =Who's Who| publisher =A & C Black| isbn =978-0-7136-7527-6| url =http://www.knowuk.co.uk/| access-date =2021-02-13| archive-date =2008-05-16| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20080516081041/http://www.knowuk.co.uk/| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

在職業生涯的早期，平诺克亦演奏當代作曲家的大鍵琴作品，包括[[罗伯托·格哈德|格哈德]]、[[曼努埃尔·德·法雅|法雅]]、[[弗朗克·马丁|马丁]]、[[弗朗西斯·普朗克|普朗克]]等人的協奏曲<ref name=crd/><ref name=poulenc>{{Cite news| last = Richmond| first = Jonathan| title = Sparkling performance of wotty Poulenc by Pinnock| newspaper = The Tech| volume = 111| issue = 55| date = 1991-12-03| url = http://tech.mit.edu/V111/N55/bso.55a.html| accessdate = 2021-02-13| archive-date = 2020-08-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809110857/http://tech.mit.edu/V111/N55/bso.55a.html| dead-url = no}} – He performed and recorded the ''Concert Champêtre'' in 1991.</ref>。2000年，平诺克與[[马克西姆·文格洛夫|马克西姆·文格洛夫]]一同巡迴演出，過程中平诺克首次接觸現代鋼琴，文格洛夫亦嘗試以巴洛克琴演奏<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.culturekiosque.com/klassik/concert/rheveng.html| title = Maxim Vengerov: Baroque Violinist| access-date = 2007-04-26| last = Sidgwick| first = John| date = 2000-03-29| work = Culturekiosque Klassiknet| archive-date = 2000-07-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20000706193715/http://www.culturekiosque.com/klassik/concert/rheveng.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://arts.guardian.co.uk/reviews/story/0,,700216,00.html|title = Baroque adventure|access-date = 2007-04-26|last = Service|first = Tom|date = 2000-02-16|work = [[衛報|''The Guardian'']]|archive-date = 2008-01-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080105122818/http://arts.guardian.co.uk/reviews/story/0,,700216,00.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

;英國古樂團
1972年11月，{{link-en|英國古樂團|The English Concert}}成立，他們使用當代樂器演奏，曲目則專注於巴洛克與古典時期作品<ref name=gramophone/>{{notetag|大約在同一時期，[[克利斯朵夫·霍格伍德|克利斯朵夫·霍格伍德]]創建了同樣專於古樂演奏的團體「{{link-en|古乐学院乐团|Academy of Ancient Music}}」。}}。起始成員僅7人，但迅速壯大。對於專事[[復古風格演奏|古樂演奏]]的決定，平诺克回憶<ref name=autumn>{{Cite news| last = Marceau| first = Guy| title = Trevor Pinnock – Autumn Thoughts| newspaper = La Scena Musicale| volume = 10| issue = 1| date = 2004-09-09| url = http://www.scena.org/lsm/sm10-1/Trevor-Pinnock-en.htm| accessdate = 2021-02-13| archive-date = 2016-03-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213512/http://www.scena.org/lsm/sm10-1/Trevor-Pinnock-en.htm| dead-url = no}} "When the members of the English Concert were looking for a new conductor and artistic director, they decided on Andrew Manze, and I think they made a good choice. But it was their decision."</ref>：

{{quotation|我當時認為，應該繼續對未知的領域進行探索。現時固然有很多傑出的巴洛克音樂詮釋（用的是現代樂器），我感覺這方法已然到了盡頭，但前方仍有許多的可能性。[[尼古劳斯·哈农库特|尼古劳斯·哈农库特]]與古斯塔夫·莱昂哈特對此做了許多有趣的實驗，我們則應該以自己的方法繼續下去。在今天，古樂器演奏相較以前已容易了許多，經歷一番掙扎，許多難題得以解決。然而，現在的演奏者們已經有相當好的技術，下一代音樂家們的道路則由我們來開創。}}

[[File:Trevor_Pinnock_2.jpg|thumb]]
平诺克是古樂演奏與巴洛克曲目振興的先鋒人物，[[伦纳德·伯恩斯坦|伦纳德·伯恩斯坦]]相當肯定他的活動：「平诺克的作品令我感到興奮！特別是他的巴赫和韓德爾，簡直讓人坐不住！」<ref>{{Cite book| last =Cott| first =Jonathan| date =2003-04-01| title =Back to a Shadow in the Night: Music Journalism and Writings: 1968–2001| publisher =Hal Leonard| edition =1st| isbn =0-634-03596-7| page =[https://archive.org/details/backtoshadowinni00cott/page/207 207]| url =https://archive.org/details/backtoshadowinni00cott/page/207}}</ref>

1973年，英國古樂團在倫敦巴赫音樂節初次登場<ref name=grove>{{cite web| title =Pinnock, Trevor| access-date =2007-05-01| last =Pratt| first =George| work =Grove Music Online| url =https://www.oxfordmusiconline.com/grovemusic/abstract/10.1093/gmo/9781561592630.001.0001/omo-9781561592630-e-0000043632?rskey=iRR9i4&result=1| editor =L. Macy| archive-date =2020-08-10| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200810165158/https://www.oxfordmusiconline.com/grovemusic/abstract/10.1093/gmo/9781561592630.001.0001/omo-9781561592630-e-0000043632?rskey=iRR9i4&result=1| dead-url =no}}</ref>。1975年，在[[约翰·艾略特·加德纳|约翰·艾略特·加德纳]]的指導下，他們演出了[[让-菲利普·拉莫|拉摩]]最後的劇作《{{link-fr|北方人 (歌剧)|Les Boréades|北方人}}》<ref>{{cite journal | journal= Early Music | first=Robert |last=Donington | title=Rameau's ''Les Boréades'' | page=263 | year=1975 |volume=3 | issue=3 | doi=10.1093/earlyj/3.3.263}}</ref>。1980年，平诺克第一次在[[逍遥音乐会|逍遥音乐会]]亮相。1983年，他隨團巡迴北美。1986年，他們演出了韓德爾《所羅門》，之後更上演了許多大型作品<ref name=hutchinson/>。平诺克與樂團繼而巡迴世界各地，旅行演奏之餘亦完成了許多錄音。評論認為平诺克「擁有獨樹一幟的活力與熱情，使聽眾易於接受」<ref name=grove/>。

值得一提的是，英國古樂團曾經為了演出拉摩的《{{Link-en|西巴里斯人|Acante et Céphise}}》（''Acante et Céphise''）（1963年）而臨時成立合唱團。九〇年代中期，樂團演出巴赫[[B小調彌撒曲|B小調彌撒]]，將合唱團重新納入正式編組中，此後便持續成長。合唱團的加入使英國古樂團得以常態性地演出巴洛克時期的歌劇、神劇以及其它人聲作品，包括一系列的巴赫曲目等<ref name=goldberg>{{cite journal| title = Interview : The English Concert| last = Argent| first = Mark| date = 25 October 2005-10-25| journal = Goldberg Magazine}}</ref>。

在指導樂團逾卅年的時間裏，平诺克通常兼任大鍵琴（或者小型管風琴）演奏；在他看來，指揮是屬於19世紀的角色與職務<ref>"Trevor’s preference was always to direct from the keyboard. He regarded the conductor as an essentially 19th century invention." – Felix Warnock, see above</ref>。2003年，在成員的共同決議下，由小提琴家[[安德魯·曼澤|安德魯·曼澤]]接手樂團指導<ref name=autumn/><ref name=guardian>{{cite web| url = http://arts.guardian.co.uk/reviews/story/0,,994757,00.html| title = English Concert/Pinnock| access-date = 2007-04-14| last = Jeal| first = Erica| date = 2003-07-08| work = ''The Guardian''| archive-date = 2008-01-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080105122823/http://arts.guardian.co.uk/reviews/story/0,,994757,00.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。對此他表示<ref name=torch>{{cite web| url = http://www.andante.com/article/article.cfm?id=16111| title = Passing the (Authentic 18th-Century) Torch: Andrew Manze Succeeds Trevor Pinnock as Director of The English Concert| access-date = 2007-04-15| last = Vickers| first = David| date = | work = andante| deadurl = yes| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070811222719/http://www.andante.com/article/article.cfm?id=16111| archive-date = 2007-08-11}}</ref>：

{{quotation|我還有其他想做的事⋯⋯一年和樂團有18至20周的時間在一起，其餘則是客席指揮，犧牲的則是能夠演奏大鍵琴的時間。我決定要邁向下一階段，或許完成一些獨奏曲目。與其在我六十歲已經做不動的時候，不如現在就做出決斷。⋯⋯有許多曲目是我想重新演奏的，尤其是英國曲目，例如Thomas Tomkins、[[威廉·伯德|William Byrd]]、John Bull和[[奥兰多·吉本斯|Orlando Gibbons]]等等。}}

;其它活動
1989年，平诺克在紐約創建了「古典合奏團」（The Classical Band），並與[[德意志留声机|DG]]簽訂合同，預計錄製18張唱片<ref>{{cite web| url = https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CE5DD173EF934A25757C0A966958260| title = Review/Music; 2 Nights, 2 Ensembles And Much Mozart| access-date = 2007-04-14| last = Kozinn| first = Allan| date = 1990-04-17| work = The New York Times| quote = The Classical Band was born last year with the music world equivalent of a silver spoon.| archive-date = 2012-10-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005061818/https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0CE5DD173EF934A25757C0A966958260| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在他的規劃下，樂團演出古典、早期浪漫時期（海頓至孟德爾頌）的曲目，同樣使用當代樂器。有時，平诺克亦會擔任古鋼琴演奏<ref>{{cite web| url = https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DEFDA163DF931A25756C0A96F948260| title = Review/Concert; Pinnock and New Ensemble Play Mozart as He Heard It| access-date = 2007-04-14| last = Henahan| first = Donal| date = 1989-05-12| work = The New York Times| archive-date = 2012-10-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005061830/https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DEFDA163DF931A25756C0A96F948260| dead-url = no}} – A review of The Classical Band's debut.</ref>。不過在一些反應不佳的演出之後，他與樂團拆夥，其職務則由[[布魯諾·懷爾|布魯諾·懷爾]]繼承<ref>{{cite web| url = https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D0CEFDA1F38F933A2575BC0A967958260| title = Review/Music; Authenticity: No More a Goal in Itself| access-date = 2007-04-14| last = Rothstein| first = Edward| date = 1991-08-10| work = The New York Times| archive-date = 2012-10-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005061835/https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9D0CEFDA1F38F933A2575BC0A967958260| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

1991至1996年期間，他是[[加拿大国家艺术中心乐团|加拿大国家艺术中心乐团]]的藝術總監、首席指揮<ref name=nac>National Arts Centre [https://www.nac-cna.ca/en/news/viewnews.cfm?ID=1537&cat=catNACO Esteemed Baroque interpreter Trevor Pinnock leads the NAC Orchestra's 2007 Messiah on  18–19 December] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20110706190822/https://www.nac-cna.ca/en/news/viewnews.cfm?ID=1537&cat=catNACO |date=2011-07-06 }} [Accessed 2007-12-11]</ref>，並續任其藝術顧問至1998年止。他與該樂團進行了美國巡迴，並錄製了貝多芬第1號、第5號鋼琴協奏曲<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rogev.com/sokolov/reviews/Sokolov%20records%20Beethoven.htm| title = Russian pianist enjoys harmonious relationship with NAC| access-date = 2007-04-14| last = Mazey| first = Steven| date = 1996-07-16| work = Ottawa Citizen| deadurl=yes| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070213030823/http://www.rogev.com/sokolov/reviews/Sokolov%20records%20Beethoven.htm| archive-date = 2007-02-13}}</ref>{{notetag|與[[格里戈里·利普马诺维奇·索科洛夫|格里戈里·索科洛夫]]合作，錄音並未公開發行。}}。

除上述工作外，他在世界主要樂團亦有指揮紀錄，包括：[[波士顿交响乐团|波士頓]]、舊金山、底特律、洛杉磯、[[芝加哥交响乐团|芝加哥]]等美國樂團，歐陸方面有[[伯明翰市立交響樂團|伯明翰市立交響樂團]]、{{link-de|弗萊堡巴洛克樂團|Freiburger Barockorchester}}、{{link-de|薩爾茨堡莫扎特大學管弦樂團|Mozarteumorchester Salzburg}}、[[柏林爱乐乐团|柏林爱乐]]、[[维也纳爱乐乐团|维也纳爱乐]]、[[伦敦爱乐乐团|伦敦爱乐]]、[[萊比錫布商大廈管弦樂團|萊比錫布商大廈管弦樂團]]、[[不来梅德意志室内爱乐乐团|不来梅德意志室内爱乐乐团]]<ref name=ebe>European Brandenburg Ensemble [http://www.europeanbrandenburg.com/About_Trevor_Pinnock.htm Trevor Pinnock] {{Wayback|url=http://www.europeanbrandenburg.com/About_Trevor_Pinnock.htm |date=20200809163622 }}. Retrieved 2010-02-18.</ref>，亞洲則有水戶室內樂團<ref>Tetsuya Sekine (2001) [http://www.arttowermito.or.jp/music/pinnockint.html MCO The 48th Regular Concert Interview with Maestro Trevor Pinnock] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060207144539/http://www.arttowermito.or.jp/music/pinnockint.html |date=2006-02-07 }}, Mito Art Tower. Retrieved 2010-02-16.</ref>⋯⋯等等。

平诺克亦是檀格塢、薩爾茨堡等地的音樂節常客<ref name=grove/><ref name=AskonasHolt />。1988年，平诺克首次在紐約[[大都會歌劇院|大都會歌劇院]]指揮演出，當晚劇目為韓德爾的《{{Link-en|朱利奧·凱撒|Giulio Cesare}}》（''Giulio Cesare''）。同年，他在薩爾茨堡音樂節第一次登台，指揮韓德爾《[[弥赛亚_(亨德尔)|弥赛亚]]》<ref name=debrett/><ref name=hutchinson/><ref>{{Cite web|title=SALZBURGER FESTSPIELE ARCHIV - PROGRAMMDETAIL|url=https://archive.salzburgerfestspiele.at/archivdetail/programid/1947/id/0/sid/17|accessdate=2021-02-13|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=de}}</ref>。2005年，在[[悉尼歌剧院|悉尼歌剧院]]指揮韓德爾的《[[里纳尔多|里納爾多]]》（''Rinaldo''）<ref name=ford>Ford, Andrew "[http://www.abc.net.au/rn/music/mshow/s1458221.htm Trevor Pinnock discusses Handel's Rinaldo] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110619051701/http://www.abc.net.au/rn/music/mshow/s1458221.htm |date=2011-06-19 }}". Retrieved 2010-02-16.</ref>{{notetag|該場演出中，他亦演奏了由{{link-en|威廉·巴貝爾|William Babell}}所改編的一些詠唱調，巴貝爾本人則宣稱這些堪稱炫技的改編，是出自於韓德爾本人之手<ref>Carey Beebe Harpsichords, A [http://www.hpschd.nu/s/rinaldo-s.html sound clip] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hpschd.nu/s/rinaldo-s.html |date=20151018080629 }} of part of the 'Vò far guerra' from Act II of ''Rinaldo'', with Emma Matthews and Trevor Pinnock directing the Australian Opera & Ballet Orchestra from the harpsichord. Retrieved 2010-02-16.</ref>。}}。

=== 近年 ===
[[File:Trevor_Pinnock_3.jpg|thumb]]
2003年之後，平诺克將他的時間均分於大鍵琴演奏與指揮，他的指揮活動則不再侷限於使用古樂器的團體。2007年，平诺克與歐洲布蘭登堡合奏團在歐洲、遠東地區巡迴，該團是為他的六十歲生日而特別設立的，他與該樂團錄製了[[约翰·塞巴斯蒂安·巴赫|巴赫]]《[[勃兰登堡协奏曲|勃兰登堡协奏曲]]》全本（獲得2008年[[留声机奖|留聲機唱片獎]]<ref>[http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article4825370.ece 2008 Gramophone Award Winners] {{Wayback|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article4825370.ece |date=20110414171021 }}, ''Times online'', 2008-09-25. Retrieved 2010-02-13.</ref>），也演出受歡迎的巴洛克時期作品<ref name="Church">{{cite web|url=http://enjoyment.independent.co.uk/music/features/article2073176.ece |title=Happy Bach day to you, Mr Pinnock |access-date=2007-04-27 |last=Church |first=Michael |date=2006-12-14 |work=The Independent }}{{dead link|date=June 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://thestar.com.my/lifestyle/story.asp?file=/2007/4/22/lifearts/17496152&sec=lifearts| title = Baroque balm| access-date = 2007-04-27| last = Cheah| first = Jason| date = 2006-04-22| work = The Star (Malaysia)| deadurl = yes| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521054939/http://thestar.com.my/lifestyle/story.asp?file=%2F2007%2F4%2F22%2Flifearts%2F17496152&sec=lifearts| archive-date = 2011-05-21}}</ref><ref>European Brandenburg Ensemble [http://www.europeanbrandenburg.com/Concerts_EuroFarEast.htm 2007 Concert Dates] {{Wayback|url=http://www.europeanbrandenburg.com/Concerts_EuroFarEast.htm |date=20200809134329 }}. Retrieved 2010-02-15.</ref>。

此外，他亦興起了對教育的興趣<ref name=AskonasHolt>Askonas Holt [http://www.askonasholt.co.uk/artists/conductors/trevor-pinnock Trevor Pinnock] {{Wayback|url=http://www.askonasholt.co.uk/artists/conductors/trevor-pinnock |date=20160303171510 }} Retrieved 2010-02-15.</ref>。於皇家音樂學院<ref>Royal Academy of Music, [http://www.ram.ac.uk/study/selectadepartment/biogs/pages/trevor%20pinnock%20cbe.aspx Trevor Pinnock CBE] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ram.ac.uk/study/selectadepartment/biogs/pages/trevor%20pinnock%20cbe.aspx |date=20100924150504 }}, staff biographies. Retrieved 2010-02-18.</ref>、[[萨尔茨堡莫扎特音乐大学|萨尔茨堡莫扎特音乐大学]]、[[香港演藝學院|香港演藝學院]]<ref name=AskonasHolt />等校開設大師班與工作坊。{{Link-en|拉爾斯·烏爾里克·莫滕森|Lars Ulrik Mortensen}}、尼古拉斯·帕爾（Nicholas Parle）、卡洛爾·西拉希（Carole Cerasi）、{{Link-en|朱利安·柏金斯|Julian Perkins}}等大鍵琴演奏家皆是他的學生。

